subject: utiX - Ecore_X: get rid of utilx and Ecore_X
commitMessage:
utiX - Ecore_X: get rid of utilx and Ecore_X

Remote the use of utilX and replaces it for efl_util (the new wrappers
added to prepare for wayland support), and conditionally build where wayland
is not yet supported.

Signed-off-by: Leandro Dorileo <leandro.maciel.dorileo@intel.com>

comments.message:
Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1

Looks good to me. But, with this patch, it still can't build  against X free repo (http://download.tizen.org/snapshots/devel/wayland/mobile/latest/repos/mobile/ia32/packages/). We may need more patches to fully remove the X dependency.
